title: Consumed
description: In this Dateline classic, a home in Kentucky is ravaged by fire in the middle of the night. Firefighters work their way to the master bedroom where they make a grisly discovery. Dennis Murphy reports. Originally aired on NBC on April 8, 2016.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
